Title: Spyborgs_PAL_WII-MOMENT
Date: 21/09/09
System: WII
Region: PAL
Language: ENG
Web: http://www.tothegame.com/wii-8152-spyborgs-for-nintendo-wii.html
Info: 
Players jump between the identities of a team of five bionic superspies 
to combat a rogue squad of wacky, dysfunctional super villains. Each 
character has unique powers to match their super-spy skills, such as 
heavy firepower, martial arts, bladed weaponry, acrobatic skateboarding 
skills or pure robotic destruction. This cast of characters may make a 
misfit group individually, but by utilizing them as a team, the Spyborgs 
will have the power to save the world û if they don't blow themselves up 
first! Spyborgs' tongue-in-cheek action and compelling interactive 
cartoon theme keeps players engaged from the first episode to the last 
with one of the most fun and entertaining games to be developed for the 
Wii system.
